Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:07.73,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,200)\fad(800,800)}干\N劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是各种没干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是高中生哦  而且还是新学期哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲什么的只要去做就自然会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是连「去做」的干劲都拿不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才能拿出「去做」这样的干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「去做」的干劲吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.10,0:00:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  总之就得去干！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想做一个单纯的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  差不多该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:53.66,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的早饭是烤鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我要吃蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是吃过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼里面可是有大量营养的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑食的话可是长不大…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那可是我们重要的早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不…不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可绝对不是机器人般的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定那只猫也有着自己的难处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撞上了～
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}小芥子人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小芥子人偶（こけし）江户时代末期开始出现的日本东北地区的温泉特产及乡土玩具\N一般形态为球形头部和圆柱形身子，没有四肢。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}红牛玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:59.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}红牛玩偶（赤べこ）福岛县会津地区的乡土玩具，「べこ」是东北方言「牛」的意思\N整体涂红，头部会摆动，是祝愿小孩子茁壮成长的吉祥物。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}鲑鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Selamat pagi:印尼语早上好的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  祐子  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  我忘记带学生证了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  Selamat pagi被无视了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不想被高年级学生叫出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种时候  只要说「我是三年级学生」不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可解决不了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  打雷？  明明是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会突然掉下什么东西来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是雷阵雨  冰雹之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芥子人偶…从天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会是小芥子人偶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳  这是从哪儿掉下来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啦  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在人生中被小芥子人偶砸到的几率很小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没有不是吗  那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近于零了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来说  也许会走运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走运个头啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会是红牛玩偶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红牛玩偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  并不是没有走运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样想就行了  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有被生鲜的东西砸到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想来  那可真是不幸中的万幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鲑鱼啊！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你在看什么书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房地产的情报杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  麻衣要搬家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  Selamat pagi又被无视了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 今天要在之后唱摇篮曲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Selamat malam:印尼语晚上好的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat malam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你应该说Selamat pagi才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  什么语言？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班…班会要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  今早来学校的时候  发现这个在鞋箱里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁知道是谁放进去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  要是有谁知道的话  请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  会是谁呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是恶作剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是喜欢老师的学生之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不会放弥勒菩萨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我也不是无法了解那种暗恋的仰慕之情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像美绪对笹原学长的思念一样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士一定在担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小炭炉点着火放在那里也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  下不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  筷子不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木屐也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  连手也没了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我会被别人发现是机器人的
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:31.09,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,300)\fad(800,0)\fs25}W\No\Nn\Nd\Ne\Nr\Nf\Nu\Nl
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  再不快点吃的话就要打午休铃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你不喜欢吃小香肠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃便当的时候把最美味的留在最后这是基本常识哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是用「美味」作结束语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来  我要开动啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.83,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,290)\fad(800,800)}日\N常\N之\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早得很呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…出局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  美绪  三秒规则哦  三秒规则
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你那是彻彻底底出局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出你满满的能量哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:21.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}甩绳者头戴的是中之条家的大福头套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入春季  新的一年就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气候还在持续寒冷中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是比同学们要冷得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:41.15,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,160)\fad(600,0)}日常之3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之希望大家不要感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  这是大家与校长我的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家不听我的话  校长我就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去别的学校当别人的校长了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  交头接耳会被批评的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么  校长没有意识到自己的冷笑话太老土了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都没有人笑  他自己应该是最清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  难讲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是想把  明知道大家没有笑还在不断努力的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现给现在的年轻人们看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那样  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位校长…就太厉害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是对那种老头儿冷笑话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我是第一次看到麻衣笑得这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  这里让我来吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有种一开口就会失去一切的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在她发现之前…还是不要拿下来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}触手
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来有请樱井老师为大家进行辅导
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井老师  交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  樱井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我是学生辅导员樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这么多人面前会紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多久都无法接近我成为理想中的教师的目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说的时候  就要一股脑儿说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在学校经常看到山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家不要把山羊带到学校来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山羊  山羊有什么错！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑山羊来上学并没有违反校规不是吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  那不是笹原学长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  那就…那就允许骑山羊来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驳回啦  驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部驳回！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能够带山羊来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那样说  立花美里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我要用我尊贵的双足走着上学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  笹原家的长男可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原家的长男算什么玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们家不过是普通农家罢了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样  长男说自己是长男有什么不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  笹原家里原来是农家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有种被骗了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只停在自行车场的山羊  原来是笹原学长带来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑着白色山羊的笹原学长…来迎接我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  new  year
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me  Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  边骑自行车边打手机是非常危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…最后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上我在自己的鞋箱里发现了弥勒菩萨像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这种恶作剧是不可取的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒菩萨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  请不要突然停下来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这处  说不定就是所谓的既视感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会生气的  请举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有人承认的话  今天的早会就一直开下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  因为我听说今天是樱井老师的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒菩萨像是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:07.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}5-7-5的俳句格式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为会很适合  而送出礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果弥勒菩萨像  被完全抛弃  by校长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么早会到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我们校长至今为止的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教导主任！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.75,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,250)\fad(600,800)}按\N钮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个消防栓的按钮看上去很有想去按的魔力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  噗噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你试着按一下吧  之前按的时候没有发出声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  要逃出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  总之先到学校空地上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙推什么推啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在推我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前早就看你这家伙不顺眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了  也许会有人死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吵等下再吵
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:08.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}Helvetica Standard：日常原作者あらゐけいいち以自己的同人社团「ヒマラヤイルカ」的\N名义创作的同人志2009年8月23日发行，内容为WEB日记漫画「Helvetica Standard」的总集篇。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请问KY是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  KY到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请告诉我KY方面的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  队长  KY是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}KY为空気が読めない的略写，即不解风情
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:43.16,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,340)\fad(300,0)\fs30}重\N要\N的\N事\N与\N该\N做\N的\N事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年B班笹原幸治郎同学  请火速到办公室富冈老师处来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说确实是没有违反校规
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是山羊也太那啥了吧  山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有别的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意徒步的话  骑自行车也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是山羊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫富冈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富冈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加上老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你就不能不叫它山羊  叫它笹原小次郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在它还是羊啊
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:22.44,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,290)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做东云名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和我一起生活的博士制造出的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士好像在进行着某种研究  整天都待在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我照顾着博士  度过着每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  牛奶冲好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么出众的功能却有痛觉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士  碰到小趾了  碰到小趾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小趾…趾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这样就应该没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有出众的功能小趾却能摘下来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  这个发条是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  还没有转过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会转转看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样转的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  看来我有很多出众的功能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  很有趣对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非就只是为了这个而装了发条…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非就只是为了这个而装了发条？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把发条取下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为装了发条很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的  请马上摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…明明很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能变得更加普通就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像普通人一样坐在椅子上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉的时候可以随意翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  连学校都没法去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不做成人形机器人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的  我是骗你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也就是芥川龙之介赏，是为了纪念日本文豪芥川龙之介而设立的文学奖项
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去给我拿个芥川奖来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要芥川奖  我要芥川奖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}就是这样的日常风景
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是名乃的大拇趾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容量为1GB
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好的容量大小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请期待下回的日常第二话
