Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:50.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まさか　いや　片思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.50,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an4}両\N思\Nい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:52.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やばい！　視線会合っちゃた！！！
