Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:44.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}觉\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:46.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N个\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:50.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道  不对  是单相思
