Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初恋！  在平日的上学路上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飞翔般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:48.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
